snippet.textDisplay:
Thank you so much Coke Studio for an amazing season. You began with awesome numbers like Aaqa and Maula e Qul and you ended up with Rang featuring Shaheed Amjad Sabri and RFAK! It was heartbreaking to believe that Amjad Sabri isn't between us anymore but by bringing such a spiritual kalaam it felt like we found a closure to his departure, brought tears to my eyes. BIG LOSS  FOR US..........WE  NEVER  FORGET  YOU.....................

Hats off for bringing us a season to stay hooked to for a long time, take a bow, too!❤️❤️❤️
